  }, "v5"), mdx("p", null, "Sau \u0111\xF3 Gi\xEA-r\xEA-mi b\u1EA3o Ba-r\xFAc, \"Ta b\u1ECB c\u1EA3n tr\u1EDF, kh\xF4ng th\u1EC3 \u0111i v\xE0o \u0111\u1EC1n th\u1EDD CH\xDAA \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c. Ta ph\u1EA3i \u1EDF l\u1EA1i \u0111\xE2y. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v6"
  }, "v6"), mdx("p", null, "Cho n\xEAn ta mu\u1ED1n ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111i v\xE0o \u0111\u1EC1n th\u1EDD CH\xDAA v\xE0o ng\xE0y m\xE0 d\xE2n ch\xFAng c\u1EEF \u0103n. \u0110\u1ECDc nh\u1EEFng l\u1EDDi trong cu\u1ED9n s\xE1ch cho d\xE2n Giu-\u0111a t\u1EEB c\xE1c th\u1ECB tr\u1EA5n \u0111\u1EBFn Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem. H\xE3y \u0111\u1ECDc nh\u1EEFng l\u1EDDi c\u1EE7a CH\xDAA, l\xE0 nh\u1EEFng l\u1EDDi ng\u01B0\u01A1i vi\u1EBFt tr\xEAn cu\u1ED9n gi\u1EA5y m\xE0 ta \u0111\xE3 \u0111\u1ECDc cho ng\u01B0\u01A1i. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v7"
  }, "v7"), mdx("p", null, "C\xF3 th\u1EC3 h\u1ECD s\u1EBD c\u1EA7u xin CH\xDAA gi\xFAp m\xECnh. C\xF3 th\u1EC3 m\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi s\u1EBD th\xF4i l\xE0m \u0111i\u1EC1u \xE1c v\xEC CH\xDAA \u0111\xE3 tuy\xEAn b\u1ED1 Ng\xE0i r\u1EA5t t\u1EE9c gi\u1EADn h\u1ECD.\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v8"
  }, "v8"), mdx("p", null, "V\u1EADy Ba-r\xFAc, con N\xEA-ria l\xE0m m\u1ECDi \u0111i\u1EC1u nh\xE0 ti\xEAn tri Gi\xEA-r\xEA-mi d\u1EB7n b\u1EA3o. \xD4ng \u0111\u1ECDc l\u1EDBn nh\u1EEFng l\u1EDDi c\u1EE7a CH\xDAA ghi trong cu\u1ED9n gi\u1EA5y trong \u0111\u1EC1n th\u1EDD CH\xDAA. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v9"
  }, "v9"), mdx("p", null, "V\xE0o th\xE1ng ch\xEDn n\u0103m th\u1EE9 n\u0103m \u0111\u1EDDi Gi\xEA-h\xF4-gia-kim, con Gi\xF4-xia l\xE0m vua, th\xEC ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ta loan b\xE1o m\u1ED9t th\u1EDDi k\u1EF3 \u0111\u1EB7c bi\u1EC7t c\u1EEF \u0103n. T\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 d\xE2n c\u01B0 Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem v\xE0 m\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi t\u1EEB c\xE1c th\u1ECB tr\u1EA5n Giu-\u0111a \u0111\u1EBFn Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem \u0111\u1EC1u c\u1EEF \u0103n \u0111\u1EC3 t\xF4n k\xEDnh CH\xDAA. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v10"
  }, "v10"), mdx("p", null, "L\xFAc \u0111\xF3 Ba-r\xFAc \u0111\u1ECDc cho m\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u1EDF \u0111\xF3 nghe nh\u1EEFng l\u1EDDi c\u1EE7a Gi\xEA-r\xEA-mi trong cu\u1ED9n s\xE1ch. \xD4ng \u0111\u1ECDc cu\u1ED9n s\xE1ch n\u01A1i \u0111\u1EC1n th\u1EDD CH\xDAA trong ph\xF2ng c\u1EE7a Gh\xEA-ma-ria, con Sa-phan, m\u1ED9t b\xED th\u01B0 ho\xE0ng gia. Ph\xF2ng \u0111\xF3 n\u1EB1m tr\xEAn s\xE2n ngay l\u1ED1i v\xE0o C\u1ED5ng M\u1EDBi c\u1EE7a \u0111\u1EC1n th\u1EDD. "), mdx("h6", {
