  }, "v11"), mdx("p", null, "Mi-cai-gia, con Gh\xEA-ma-ria, ch\xE1u Sa-phan nghe nh\u1EEFng l\u1EDDi c\u1EE7a CH\xDAA ghi trong cu\u1ED9n s\xE1ch. "), mdx("h6", {
